  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK323">
<l>oṉṟāka nallatu kollāmai maṟṟataṉ</l>
<l>piṉcārap poyyāmai naṉṟu.</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not to destroy life is an incomparably (great) good next to it in goodness ranks freedom from falsehood.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
